Ako zadatak ne kaže točnu aplikaciju, uzmeš poznati app + DB primjer, npr. WordPress + MySQL.

Cijelo rješenje naredbama
mkdir -p ~/lo3-task4-app-db
cd ~/lo3-task4-app-db

cat > compose.yaml <<'EOF'
services:
  db:
    image: docker.io/library/mysql:8.0
    container_name: task4-mysql
    environment:
      MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD: root-pw
      MYSQL_DATABASE: appdb
      MYSQL_USER: appuser
      MYSQL_PASSWORD: app-pw
    volumes:
      
db_data:/var/lib/mysql
  networks:
backend

  app:
    image: docker.io/library/wordpress:latest
    container_name: task4-wordpress
    depends_on:
      
db
  environment:
    WORDPRESS_DB_HOST: db:3306
    WORDPRESS_DB_USER: appuser
    WORDPRESS_DB_PASSWORD: app-pw
    WORDPRESS_DB_NAME: appdb
  ports:
"8080:80"
networks:
backend

volumes:
  db_data:

networks:
  backend:
EOF

Pokretanje:

podman compose up -d

Ako podman compose ne radi:

podman-compose up -d

Provjera da containeri rade:

podman ps

Provjera logova:

podman logs task4-wordpress
podman logs task4-mysql

Provjera aplikacije:

curl http://localhost:8080/

Ili otvori u browseru:

http://localhost:8080/

Provjera da je app published, a baza nije:

podman port task4-wordpress
podman port task4-mysql

Očekivanje:

task4-wordpress ima 8080:80
task4-mysql nema published port

Provjera mreže:

podman network ls
podman network inspect lo3-task4-app-db_backend

Ako network ima malo drugačije ime, uzmeš ime iz podman network ls.

Resource usage containera

Ovo je dio koji se traži za usporedbu s VM-om:

podman stats --no-stream

Možeš dodatno:

podman inspect task4-wordpress
podman inspect task4-mysql
Resource usage VM-a
Ne dižeš novu VM. Ti si već u Algebra VM-u. Samo pokažeš resurse cijelog VM okruženja:

free -h
df -h
lscpu
uptime
